│ instructions and further                                                 │
│ 16361 /// analysis/transformations.                                      │
│ 16362 /// The class also will look through the previously emitted        │
│ shuffle instructions                                                     │
│ 16363 /// and properly mark indices in mask as undef.                    │
│ 16364 /// For example, given the code                                    │
│ 16365 /// \code                                                          │
│ 16366 /// %s1 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, poison, <1, 0>                │
│ 16367 /// %s2 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %1, poison, <1, 0>                │
│ 16368 /// \endcode                                                       │
│ 16369 /// and if need to emit shuffle of %s1 and %s2 with mask <1, 0, 3, │
